prestige_Jump_Pack_Temp.display_help: This Jump Pack grants you the ability to not only jump great distances, but also jump and gain altitude in mid air! The Jump Pack will automatically shut down after 30 seconds of continuous use.

prestige_Pocket_D_VIP_Pass.display_help: You've been given a VIP Pass to Pocket D. It will allow you to access Pocket D from anywhere. It is usable once every 30 minutes.
prestige_Pocket_D_VIP_Pass.display_confirm: Activating this power will revert you to your native alignment. Proceed?

prestige_Base_Teleport.display_help: You have a Base Transport beacon. It will allow you to return to your base from any location. It is usable once every 30 minutes.

prestige_Mission_Teleport.display_help: You have a Mission Transport beacon. It will allow you to teleport to your active mission's entrance.

Team_Transporter.display_help: Activating this power will summon a vehicle that will allow your party to teleport to the active mission. This power cannot be activated while on a PvP or mission map.

prestige_Team_Recall.display_help: This power allows you to teleport all of your teammates to your location. Recharge: Very Long
prestige_Team_Recall.display_confirm: {PlayerSource} would like to Teleport you. Do you Accept?

Prestige_Ninja_Run.display_help: A combination of quickness and acrobatic grace, Ninja Run allows you to move at high speed, whether on the ground or leaping from rooftop to rooftop. This power is not as fast as Super Speed, nor will it allow you to jump as well as Super Leap, however it is considerably better than the Fitness powers Swift and Hurdle.

Prestige_Beast_Run.display_help: Show off your bestial nature by using this power. This power is not as fast as Super Speed, nor will it allow you to jump as well as Super Leap, however it is considerably better than the Fitness powers Swift and Hurdle.

Prestige_Steam_Jump.display_help: Your steam powered jump pack grants you the ability to not only jump great distances, but also jump and gain altitude in mid air! The steam powered jump pack will automatically shut down after 30 seconds of continuous use.

Alt_Hover_Board.display_help: You mount a Rocket Board allowing you to fly at great speeds. However, while this power is active you will be unable to activate most powers. Additionally this power will deactivate most powers upon activation. This power also grants the you a measure of flight protection making you less likely to be knocked out of the sky by some enemy attacks.

Alt_Magic_Carpet.display_help: You hop aboard a flying carpet allowing you to fly around with tremendous speed. However, while this power is active you will be unable to activate most powers. Additionally this power will deactivate most powers upon activation. This power also grants the you a measure of flight protection making you less likely to be knocked out of the sky by some enemy attacks.

Alt_Void_Skiff.display_help: You mount a Void Skiff allowing you to fly at great speeds. However, while this power is active you will be unable to activate most powers. Additionally this power will deactivate most powers upon activation. This power also grants the you a measure of flight protection making you less likely to be knocked out of the sky by some enemy attacks.

Alt_Coyote_Travel_Power.display_help: You transform into a coyote granting you increased movement speed and jump height. However, while this power is active you will be unable to activate most powers. Additionally this power will deactivate most powers upon activation.

Alt_Cheetah_Travel_Power.display_help: You transform into a cheetah granting you greatly increased movement speed and a slight increase to jump height. However, while this power is active you will be unable to activate most powers. Additionally this power will deactivate most powers upon activation.

Alt_Panther_Travel_Power.display_help: You transform into a Panther granting you increased movement speed and a slight boost to your jump height. However, while this power is active you will be unable to activate most powers. Additionally this power will deactivate most powers upon activation.
